自1930年代开始，锡安广场成为政治示威和社会抗议的聚集点，当时年轻的[[犹太复国主义|犹太复国主义]]开始兴起。<ref name=balt/>从1950年代到2000年代，主要是右翼示威活动在这里上演。<ref name=public/><ref name=ynet>{{cite web|url=http://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-3477183,00.html|script-title=he:ניפגש בכיכר|language=he|trans_title=Let's Meet in the Square|work=Ynetnews|first=Michal|last=Ben Ari|date=7 December 2007|accessdate=9 March 2014|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712222137/https://www.ynet.co.il/articles/0,7340,L-3477183,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>若干示威演变成暴力冲突，比如1971年的抗议中焚烧总理[[果尔达·梅厄|果尔达·梅厄]]像；1995年的抗议反对总理[[伊扎克·拉宾|伊扎克·拉宾]]签署塔巴协议，接着数千名抗议者继续前往议会，并毁坏沿途财物。{{sfn|Pedahzur|2012|pp=148–149}} 广场上最大的示威游行包括2000年5月的抗议移交毗邻[[橄榄山|橄榄山]]的阿拉伯定居点{{sfn|Balint|2001|p=46}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-73738080.html|title=Right-Wing Demonstration at Zion Square|work=Israel Wire|date=16 May 2000|accessdate=21 March 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328212129/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-73738080.html|archive-date=2015-03-28|dead-url=yes}} (subscription)</ref>；2000年11月在[[阿克萨群众起义|阿克萨群众起义]]之初抗议[[埃胡德·巴拉克|埃胡德·巴拉克]]的“限制政策”{{sfn|Gefen|2001|p=325}}；2006年抗议总理[[埃胡德·奥尔默特|埃胡德·奥尔默特]]的政策<ref>{{cite web|url=http://crownheights.info/general/1488/anti-olmert-rally-brings-100000-to-zion-square/|title=Anti-Olmert Rally Brings 100,000 to Zion Square|date=5 February 2006|accessdate=2 March 2014|work=Crown Heights.info|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314030408/http://crownheights.info/general/1488/anti-olmert-rally-brings-100000-to-zion-square/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-141686876.html|title=Anti-Olmert Rally Brings 100,000 to Jerusalem's Zion Square|date=6 February 2006|accessdate=21 March 2014|work=Israel National News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150328212127/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-141686876.html|archive-date=2015-03-28|dead-url=yes}} (subscription)</ref>，每次都吸引大约估计10万人参加。

随着2011年8月[[雅法路|雅法路]]上的[[耶路撒冷轻轨|耶路撒冷轻轨]]开通，耶路撒冷警方停止发放在锡安广场示威的许可证，以避免破坏轻轨运行。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jpost.com/National-News/Jlem-police-deny-social-protesters-Zion-Square|title=J'lem police deny social protesters Zion Square|first=Melanie|last=Lidman|date=30 May 2012|accessdate=2 March 2014|work=[[The_Jerusalem_Post|The Jerusalem Post]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.haaretz.com/news/national/jerusalem-protesters-stopped-in-their-tracks-by-light-rail-as-zion-square-declared-off-limits-1.433033|title= Jerusalem protesters stopped in their tracks by light rail as Zion Square declared off limits|first=Nir|last=Hasson|date=29 May 2012|accessdate=9 March 2014|work=[[Haaretz|Haaretz]]}}</ref>

===恐怖袭击===
在锡安电影院曾经两度发生未遂爆炸事件，一次在1951年，另一次在1967年。<ref name=public/><ref name=balt>{{cite web|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2002-01-27/news/0201270058_1_jaffa-jerusalem-main-street|title=Mideast ideologies collide on Jerusalem's Jaffa Road|first=Peter|last=Hermann|work=[[The_Baltimore_Sun|The Baltimore Sun]]|date=27 January 2002|accessdate=4 March 2014|archive-date=2014-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314030336/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2002-01-27/news/0201270058_1_jaffa-jerusalem-main-street|dead-url=no}}</ref>1975年7月4日，一台冰箱装载5公斤炸药，在[[锡安广场爆炸案|锡安广场爆炸]]，死15人，伤77人<ref name=haaretz>{{cite web|url=http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/features/a-short-history-of-terror-1.76345|title=A Short History of Terror|first=Yair|last=Sheleg|work=Haaretz|date=3 December 2001|accessdate=3 March 2014|archive-date=2014-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140401113337/http://www.haaretz.com/print-edition/features/a-short-history-of-terror-1.76345|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1979年3月24日，一枚炸弹在锡安广场的垃圾桶爆炸，死1人，伤13人<ref name=haaretz/>。2012年8月16-17日的晚上，数十犹太青少年在锡安广场追打4名巴勒斯坦青少年，以色列警方和目击者描述为意图[[私刑|私刑]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/closeread/2012/08/an-attack-in-zion-square.html|title=An Attack in Zion Square|first=Amy|last=Davidson|work=The New Yorker|date=21 August 2012|accessdate=14 March 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |first=Isabel|last=Kershner|authorlink=Isabel Kershner|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/21/world/middleeast/7-israelis-held-in-attack-on-palestinians-in-jerusalem.html |title=Young Israelis Held in Attack on Arabs|work=The New York Times|date=20 August 2012}}</ref>。

===衰落与重建===
[[File:West_Jerusalem_Zion_Square_Bank_Hapoalim_building.jpg|thumb]]
1967年耶路撒冷的统一后，这个城市开始明显扩大。大型商业中心在远离市中心的新社区开张，将顾客从市中心吸引走。政府机构也开始迁出，带来下城三角在1970年代的经济衰退。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jiis.org/.upload/merkaz%20-%20english.pdf|title=Downtown Jerusalem: The story of Jerusalem's city center and its regeneration|first1=Amnon|last1=Ramon|first2=Aviel|last2=Yelinek|first3=Asaf|last3=Vitman|year=2011|accessdate=14 March 2014|publisher=Jerusalem Institute for Israel Studies|page=5|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203004738/http://www.jiis.org/.upload/merkaz%20-%20english.pdf|archive-date=2013-12-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>[[电视|电视]]的问世造成下城三角大部分电影院的关闭。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nrg.co.il/online/54/ART2/284/157.html|script-title=he:פעם היה פה שמח: געגועים למשולש הזהב של ירושלים|trans_title=Once It Was Happy Here: Nostalgia for the golden triangle of Jerusalem|language=he|first=Hailit|last=Kreusa-Israel|date=12 September 2011|accessdate=14 March 2014|work=Maariv|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064718/http://www.nrg.co.il/online/54/ART2/284/157.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>锡安电影院于1972年关闭并拆除。<ref name=public/>原址改建为高层建筑，上部开设Kikar 锡安酒店，下部开设 HaPoalim银行分行<ref name=public/><ref name=haman/>
。

1983年，锡安广场、本耶胡达街和下城三角其他街道改建为步行街，这是重振下城区一次成功的努力<ref name=triangle/>。

