锡安广场昼夜繁忙，聚集了各种各样的人：游客，老人移民，神学院学生，街头卖艺者，<ref name=balt/>{{sfn|Thomas|2010|p=132}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jerusalemite.net/blog/2652/stepping-sideways-in-zion-square|title=Stepping sideways in Zion Square|date=23 July 2008|accessdate=2 March 2014|publisher=jerusalemite.net|archive-date=2018-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712184103/http://www.jerusalemite.net/blog/2652/stepping-sideways-in-zion-square|dead-url=yes}}</ref>“总是人满为患，总是疯狂”。{{sfn|Barrett|1999|p=175}}辍学、不满的青年宗教移民和无家可归的青年人也出没在广场上。<ref name=action>{{cite journal|url=http://ou.org.s3.amazonaws.com/publications/ja/5763/5763fall/KIKARIST.PDF|title=Kikaristim Come Home|first=Sara|last=Bedein|journal=Jewish Action|date=Fall 2002|access-date=2016-02-11|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223743/http://ou.org.s3.amazonaws.com/publications/ja/5763/5763fall/KIKARIST.PDF|dead-url=yes}}</ref>大批俄罗斯青年移民在广场游荡，喝着伏特加<ref name=know/>。该广场还吸引了数量可观的2005年从加沙撤出的定居点青年。<ref name=know>{{cite web|url=http://www.israelnationalnews.com/Articles/Article.aspx/6614#.UxO5ifmSzkU|title=The Jerusalem You Do Not Want to Know|first=David|last=Ha'Ivri|date=15 October 2006|accessdate=3 March 2014|work=Arutz Sheva|8=Israel National News|archive-date=2019-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227184610/http://www.israelnationalnews.com/Articles/Article.aspx/6614#.UxO5ifmSzkU|dead-url=no}}</ref>

锡安广场也是吸毒者的聚集地。据估计，广场上游荡的70％的青少年吸食毒品。{{sfn|Mahdī|2003|p=71}} Kikar 锡安酒店的底层毒贩和妓女出没<ref name=there>{{cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/weekend/weekend-opinions/there-s-no-there-at-jerusalem-s-zion-square-1.467318 |title=There's no 'there' at Jerusalem's Zion Square|first=Gerard|last=Heumann|work=Haaretz|date=28 September 2012}}</ref>。

==地标==
